<plot>Lucky, the family dog, is all dressed up in his tuxedo ready to be the ring bearer at Uncle Allen's wedding. Left to sit in the convertible, while his family puts the finishing touches on their wedding finery, Lucky decides to head off into the yard for some playtime. When his owner Tom finds him he must get him cleaned up before his wife Deborah notices and they are late for the wedding.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?587002</url></doc>
